</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">
  <strong>
    <span>How to Check Export Compliance on Account</span>
  </strong>
</p>
<ol style="text-align: left;">
  <li data-uuid="25839878-c25b-4711-b3df-619d40862190">
    <p>Navigate to the<span> </span>
      <strong>Contact Details Page</strong>
    </p>
  </li>
  <li data-uuid="553014f3-a035-4eb7-9b56-8f5d8230380c">
    <p>Click on the<span> </span>
      <strong>Account Name</strong>
    </p>
  </li>
  <li data-uuid="6bfdf2e8-097f-4251-bc7c-4819cd156608">
    <p>The<span> </span>
      <strong>Account Page</strong>
      <span> </span>opens in a new subtab</p>
  </li>
  <li data-uuid="4093401a-cd63-44cb-9bff-c8e8b43bbaab">
    <p>Go to the<span> </span>
      <strong>Details</strong>
      <span> </span>section</p>
  </li>
  <li data-uuid="3de75dbf-ae3f-4d99-921e-b47a068dd788">
    <p>Find the <strong>Compliance Information</strong>
      <span> </span>section</p>
