  <li data-uuid="6691ee21-ee63-4069-acaf-d8997940eb7a">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span>Observe</span>
      <span> the “Export Compliance Block” Checkbox.</span>
    </span>
    <span> </span>
  </li>
