      <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:644,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="45" data-uuid="85037854-104f-4e12-8011-0f0bc2b77d34">
        <span>Click on any “Customer CMF” to open the corresponding record detail page. Navigate to ‘Related’ tab and there we can see ‘Customer Partners (Partner CMF)’ records and their corresponding role code.</span>
        <span> </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span>
      </li>
