    <ul style="text-align: left;">
      <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="5" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:644,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="45" data-uuid="c6ce95cf-ff74-42f9-b621-c8e58b409890">
        <span data-contrast="auto">
          <span>If the ‘Customer CMF’ record has a related ‘Customer Partner’ record with role code “AG</span>
          <span>”,</span>
          <span> then that customer CMF record is eligible as a ‘sold to’ CMF.</span>
        </span>
        <span> </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul style="text-align: left;">
      <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="6" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:644,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="45" data-uuid="39cd27e0-42c7-485c-8565-0b8f4e4a55c9">
        <span>This means that we have a valid sold to record for creating an R4C case.</span>
        <span> </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span>
      </li>
