        <span data-contrast="auto">
          <span>All ‘Customer CMF’ records which have a related ‘Customer Partner’ record (with role </span>
          <span>code :</span>
          <span> AG) can be selected as sold </span>
          <span>to .</span>
        </span>
        <span> </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
