    </ul>
    <ul style="text-align: left;">
      <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="9" data-uuid="416d1911-2027-4295-b699-08b45d5af2a0">
        <span>For selecting Sold To, we have a wild card search functionality which makes it easy to search and get the required CMF value instead of going through all the values in a dropdown.</span>
