          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">Based on the Selected Sold<span> </span>
          </span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">To</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
            <span> </span>Value, all other data will be fetched for other dropdowns.</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
        </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:276}"> </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul style="text-align: left;">
      <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="6" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="9" data-uuid="56bb9d11-901e-417f-83be-6124ee05816a">
        <span data-contrast="auto">
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">When Sold To is selected, all the other details are auto populated based on the selected ‘Sold to’ value. Values are auto populated based on the most recent case created using that particular ‘Sold To’ if there is historical data of case being created using that Sold To CMF.</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
        </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:276}"> </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul style="text-align: left;">
      <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="7" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="9" data-uuid="5a7b4748-4a41-42b0-9105-422f8464ed5e">
