          <span>All other fields in Request header details are dropdowns</span>
          <span>, if</span>
          <span> any dropdown </span>
          <span>contains</span>
          <span> a single value, it would be auto populated when agent selects a value on dependent dropdown for that dropdown.</span>
        </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:276}"> </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul style="text-align: left;">
