        <span data-contrast="auto">
          <span>Sold To Address values are </span>
          <span>determined</span>
          <span> and populated from the ‘Customer Physical Address’ records which are related to selected Sold </span>
          <span>To</span>
          <span> CMF having </span>
          <span>address</span>
          <span> type as ‘Sold to</span>
          <span>’.</span>
        </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:276}"> </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul style="text-align: left;">
