        <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">From Agent UI, we can see the address records related to selected Sold To: Go to the sold to ‘Customer CMF record’ &gt; Open the Related tab &gt;<span> </span>
        </span>
        <span data-contrast="none">
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">Customer Physical Addresses &gt; See the address Type as ‘AG/WE/RG</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">’.</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
            <span> </span>All the active addresses would be displayed for<span> </span>
          </span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">user</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
            <span> </span>to choose from.</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
        </span>
      </li>
