    <span data-contrast="none">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">In this scenario, customer is shown a popup of M</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">M<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">and corresponding CPNs. Customer can select any CPN from dropdown and<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">submit</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">. Then the selected CPNs will be populated and used for respective line items. </span>
    </span>
  </li>
  <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-font="Courier New" data-leveltext="o" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:1440,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Courier New&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[9675],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;o&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="27" data-uuid="2a718cca-a948-4c31-9c22-c783db242b17">
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}">
      <span class="TextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-contrast="none" style="color:var(--ds-text,#000000);">
        <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun" data-ccp-charstyle-defn="{&quot;ObjectId&quot;:&quot;ac0262f4-8a9e-5820-b908-2d943c5f7113|1&quot;,&quot;ClassId&quot;:1073872969,&quot;Properties&quot;:[201342446,&quot;1&quot;,201342447,&quot;5&quot;,201342448,&quot;1&quot;,201342449,&quot;1&quot;,469777841,&quot;Calibri&quot;,469777842,&quot;Arial&quot;,469777843,&quot;Calibri&quot;,469777844,&quot;Calibri&quot;,201341986,&quot;1&quot;,469769226,&quot;Calibri,Arial&quot;,268442635,&quot;22&quot;,469775450,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,201340122,&quot;1&quot;,134233614,&quot;true&quot;,469778129,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,335572020,&quot;1&quot;,469778324,&quot;Default Paragraph Font&quot;]}">If<span> </span>
        </span>
