  </li>
  <li data-uuid="a376122f-bc90-438f-a43c-91d54c4a71c7">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">The line-item data obtained as response from API is again<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">validated</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>using Item Type ‘FERT</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">’.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>If Item type of line items is not ‘FERT</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">’,</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>those line items are disabled.</span>
