<ul>
  <li data-uuid="085e347c-8b64-4114-b766-ca07cb6ad023">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun" data-ccp-charstyle-defn="{&quot;ObjectId&quot;:&quot;ac0262f4-8a9e-5820-b908-2d943c5f7113|1&quot;,&quot;ClassId&quot;:1073872969,&quot;Properties&quot;:[201342446,&quot;1&quot;,201342447,&quot;5&quot;,201342448,&quot;1&quot;,201342449,&quot;1&quot;,469777841,&quot;Aptos&quot;,469777842,&quot;&quot;,469777843,&quot;Aptos&quot;,469777844,&quot;Aptos&quot;,201341986,&quot;1&quot;,469769226,&quot;Aptos&quot;,268442635,&quot;22&quot;,469775450,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,201340122,&quot;1&quot;,134233614,&quot;true&quot;,469778129,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,335572020,&quot;1&quot;,469778324,&quot;Default Paragraph Font&quot;]}">Agent can search with one or more MM or CPN by selecting respective radio button.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop" data-ccp-charstyle-defn="{&quot;ObjectId&quot;:&quot;920dbcde-2834-5e15-a5fa-062170b236ba|1&quot;,&quot;ClassId&quot;:1073872969,&quot;Properties&quot;:[201342446,&quot;1&quot;,201342447,&quot;5&quot;,201342448,&quot;1&quot;,201342449,&quot;1&quot;,469777841,&quot;Aptos&quot;,469777842,&quot;&quot;,469777843,&quot;Aptos&quot;,469777844,&quot;Aptos&quot;,201341986,&quot;1&quot;,469769226,&quot;Aptos&quot;,268442635,&quot;22&quot;,469775450,&quot;eop&quot;,201340122,&quot;1&quot;,134233614,&quot;true&quot;,469778129,&quot;eop&quot;,335572020,&quot;1&quot;,469778324,&quot;Default Paragraph Font&quot;]}"> </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}"> </span>
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">After agent selects one option and enters the related data, he can get the related line items data by clicking on the “Search” button.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}"> </span>
  </li>
  <li data-uuid="69cf90ab-9505-4e54-9842-2ec3038c98f1">
    <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">If<span> </span>
    </span>
    <strong>
      <span data-contrast="auto">
        <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">agent searches using MM</span>
        <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">,</span>
      </span>
    </strong>
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>the data inputted by the agent would be<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">validated</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>in the SF database and then valid MM numbers are sent to MM-CPN API to get the respective CPN numbers for the MMs.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
    </span>
    <p>
      <strong>
        <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun" data-ccp-charstyle-defn="{&quot;ObjectId&quot;:&quot;ac0262f4-8a9e-5820-b908-2d943c5f7113|1&quot;,&quot;ClassId&quot;:1073872969,&quot;Properties&quot;:[201342446,&quot;1&quot;,201342447,&quot;5&quot;,201342448,&quot;1&quot;,201342449,&quot;1&quot;,469777841,&quot;Calibri&quot;,469777842,&quot;Arial&quot;,469777843,&quot;Calibri&quot;,469777844,&quot;Calibri&quot;,201341986,&quot;1&quot;,469769226,&quot;Calibri,Arial&quot;,268442635,&quot;22&quot;,469775450,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,201340122,&quot;1&quot;,134233614,&quot;true&quot;,469778129,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,335572020,&quot;1&quot;,469778324,&quot;Default Paragraph Font&quot;]}">Note: Multiple CPN Scenario:</span>
      </strong>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop" data-ccp-charstyle-defn="{&quot;ObjectId&quot;:&quot;920dbcde-2834-5e15-a5fa-062170b236ba|1&quot;,&quot;ClassId&quot;:1073872969,&quot;Properties&quot;:[201342446,&quot;1&quot;,201342447,&quot;5&quot;,201342448,&quot;1&quot;,201342449,&quot;1&quot;,469777841,&quot;Calibri&quot;,469777842,&quot;Arial&quot;,469777843,&quot;Calibri&quot;,469777844,&quot;Calibri&quot;,201341986,&quot;1&quot;,469769226,&quot;Calibri,Arial&quot;,268442635,&quot;22&quot;,469775450,&quot;eop&quot;,201340122,&quot;1&quot;,134233614,&quot;true&quot;,469778129,&quot;eop&quot;,335572020,&quot;1&quot;,469778324,&quot;Default Paragraph Font&quot;]}"> </span>
      <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}"> </span>
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-font="Courier New" data-leveltext="o" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:1440,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Courier New&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[9675],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;o&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="27" data-uuid="51955916-f298-472e-b360-8f5845dbde2f">
        <span data-contrast="none">
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">For some M</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">Ms</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">,<span> </span>
          </span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">there’s</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
            <span> </span>a chance of getting multiple CPN numbers for single MM from MM-CPN API. </span>
        </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}"> </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-font="Courier New" data-leveltext="o" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:1440,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Courier New&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[9675],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;o&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="27" data-uuid="0b2c456b-2bc8-4d60-a349-44ccb3a490e4">
        <span data-contrast="none">
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">In this scenario, customer is shown a popup of M</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">M<span> </span>
          </span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">and corresponding CPNs. Customer can select any CPN from dropdown and<span> </span>
          </span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">submit</span>
          <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">. Then the selected CPNs will be populated and used for respective line items. </span>
        </span>
        <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}"> </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li data-uuid="4aadc818-1921-4ba4-90ff-e25e05ce8263">
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}">
      <span class="TextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-contrast="none" style="color:var(--ds-text,#000000);">
        <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun" data-ccp-charstyle-defn="{&quot;ObjectId&quot;:&quot;ac0262f4-8a9e-5820-b908-2d943c5f7113|1&quot;,&quot;ClassId&quot;:1073872969,&quot;Properties&quot;:[201342446,&quot;1&quot;,201342447,&quot;5&quot;,201342448,&quot;1&quot;,201342449,&quot;1&quot;,469777841,&quot;Calibri&quot;,469777842,&quot;Arial&quot;,469777843,&quot;Calibri&quot;,469777844,&quot;Calibri&quot;,201341986,&quot;1&quot;,469769226,&quot;Calibri,Arial&quot;,268442635,&quot;22&quot;,469775450,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,201340122,&quot;1&quot;,134233614,&quot;true&quot;,469778129,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,335572020,&quot;1&quot;,469778324,&quot;Default Paragraph Font&quot;]}">If<span> </span>
        </span>
      </span>
      <span class="TextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-contrast="none" style="color:var(--ds-text,#000000);">
        <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">agent searches using CPN</span>
      </span>
      <span class="TextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-contrast="none" style="color:var(--ds-text,#000000);">
        <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">, data is sent first to MM-CPN API to get the required MMs and all the valid MMs obtained will again be<span> </span>
        </span>
        <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">validated</span>
        <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
          <span> </span>in the database to get product details. </span>
      </span>
      <span class="EOP Selected SCXW68805757 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}" style="color:var(--ds-text,#000000);"> </span>
    </span>
  </li>
  <li data-uuid="b0918a12-2199-42c4-b848-c7edf2eb35a5">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">The line-item data obtained as response from API is again<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">validated</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>using Item Type ‘FERT</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">’.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>If Item type of line items is not ‘FERT</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">’,</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>those line items are disabled.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}"> </span>
  </li>
  <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="50" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:502,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="8" data-uuid="53a22a73-2c98-48f6-9ede-ecea67d72df2">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">Then the valid line items would be displayed in the table with related product information obtained from database.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}"> </span>
  </li>
  <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="51" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:502,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="8" data-uuid="af06cd3f-81e9-4d87-8109-a2bd69509222">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">The line items which fail in validation would be shown in disabled state and validation error would be shown on ‘</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">i</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">’ icon in validation column.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}"> </span>
  </li>
  <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="52" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:502,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="8" data-uuid="b196c0c3-fe41-4766-88c6-3b3babd2ae4b">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">If all entered data fails validation, it is a hard<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">stop</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">
        <span> </span>and agent is notified via error toast message.</span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="eop"> </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}"> </span>
  </li>
  <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="53" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:502,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="8" data-uuid="4f172d84-e6a1-473a-861e-adb2f6cdd9d5">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun" data-ccp-charstyle-defn="{&quot;ObjectId&quot;:&quot;ac0262f4-8a9e-5820-b908-2d943c5f7113|1&quot;,&quot;ClassId&quot;:1073872969,&quot;Properties&quot;:[201342446,&quot;1&quot;,201342447,&quot;5&quot;,201342448,&quot;1&quot;,201342449,&quot;1&quot;,469777841,&quot;Aptos&quot;,469777842,&quot;&quot;,469777843,&quot;Aptos&quot;,469777844,&quot;Aptos&quot;,201341986,&quot;1&quot;,469769226,&quot;Aptos&quot;,268442635,&quot;22&quot;,469775450,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,201340122,&quot;1&quot;,134233614,&quot;true&quot;,469778129,&quot;normaltextrun&quot;,335572020,&quot;1&quot;,469778324,&quot;Default Paragraph Font&quot;]}">Agent can also enter the PO numbers manually in the input box for each valid line item. The entered PO number would be<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span data-ccp-charstyle="normaltextrun">validated</span>
