      <span>Without filling out the Credit Price and Reason for price change, the agent<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>can’t</span>
      <span>
        <span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>proceed</span>
      <span>
        <span> </span>to the next step with that line-item; these validations will be checked<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>on click</span>
      <span>
        <span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>of  "</span>
      <span>Save and view summary" button. </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}"> </span>
  </li>
  <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="8" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:1080,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="23" data-uuid="ed811347-69c7-4b28-8d56-bf322d921ec5">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span>If the agent enters the credit price and Reason for price change for all required line-items, then<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>on click of</span>
      <span>
        <span> </span>"Save and View summary" button, the agent will get the below popup to enter the Header Level comments for price change. </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}"> </span>
  </li>
  <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="9" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:1080,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="23" data-uuid="5a77c5e1-59a8-4143-98fa-aa75d15d64cd">
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span>This is a mandatory field to<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>proceed</span>
      <span>
        <span> </span>further. Once the agent fills in the Reason for Price Change and clicks on<span> </span>
      </span>
    </span>
    <span data-contrast="none">
      <span>Save and View Summary</span>
    </span>
    <span data-contrast="auto">
      <span>,<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>case</span>
      <span>
        <span> </span>will be<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>created</span>
      <span>
        <span> </span>and<span> </span>
      </span>
      <span>user</span>
      <span>
        <span> </span>will be navigated to the View Summary page. </span>
    </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}"> </span>
  </li>
  <li data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="10" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:1080,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="23" data-uuid="b3ce90b5-6b4c-4ef0-a905-07ce34401015">
    <span data-contrast="none">
      <span>‘Net credit Value’ of each valid line item is calculated as ‘Return Quantity’ * ‘Credit Price’ and displayed in ‘Net credit value’ column.</span>
    </span>
  </li>
</ul>
